File: The Hawks are investigating Public Protector Busisiwe Mkhwebane. * Editor's note: You can read an updated version of this breaking news story here. JOHANNESBURG - eNCA can confirm that the Hawks are investigating Public Protector Busisiwe Mkhwebane. Accountability Now Director Paul Hoffman filed a complaint against Mkhwebane. READ: Accountability Now to lay charges against Mkhwebane It accuses Mkhwebane of perjury and defeating the ends of justice. "Her conduct and the way she has been in denial is not serving the public interest in SA," said Hoffman.